2 CONC aid about a quarter to 7 of his own accord &amp;quot;I have had an extra drop of drink to accomplish the job; there is five of them gone to glory, and it is a good job&amp;quot;&amp;mdash;at about half-past 7 he said &amp;quot;I am sorry for my wif
2 CONC e and parents, but the children will be better off in heaven, if there is such a place; it is better than leaving them to the mercy of the world&amp;quot;&amp;mdash;about 9 o&amp;#39;clock he said &amp;quot;I wish I had killed the little ones out o
